<br>
&quot;Ex-Paladins: A paladin who ceases to be lawful good, who willfully commits an evil act, or who grossly violates the code of conduct loses all special abilities and spells, inculding the service of the paladin's warhorse. She also may not progress in levels as a paladin. She regains her abilities if she atones for her violations...as apropriate.&quot;<br>
<br>
SO as you can see the makers of D&amp;D were very spacific to the expectations of being a paladin.<br>
